{
  "stem": "17543.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 31.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And was a private teacher also in a suburb, quite a long way, where I went to study at the age of 11, with a teacher who also lost a job because she was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was quite a long journey to go, especially in cold weather, because I had to walk quite a distance in the snow and everything to get the bus.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after the end of the bus journey, I had to go quite a distance the same way back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, that had to stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the business had to close, because my mother didn't know what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember in Hungary they were setting up a special place for dealing with us, which was called [INAUDIBLE], which is a place, but in a different meaning of place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They specialized for dealing with Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they collected up everything worth like car, my father's car, and bicycle, fur coats, which in Hungary very cold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The people was wearing before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very natural thing to wear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even I had fur coat as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, I think, '43, sometime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my father's coat, which was fur-lined, and demanded on jewelry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother given everything what we had, but they didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember cutting open pillows and feathers everywhere, because they thought it might have been hidden jewelry there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it came the time I had to wear yellow star on our clothes, which meant for a few hours a day being able to go out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But again, I don't know if it was everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
